1 Overview

Here we report some statistics about subchallenge II and evaluate the leaderboard.

Some statistics about challenge II:

  • the number of total submissions: 77.
  • the number of submissions per rounds
    • round 1: 14
    • round 2: 42
    • round 3: 21
  • the number of teams participated in this sub challenge: 25

Nice improvement from roun 1 to round 2 and final round.

2 Leaderboards

Next figure shows all the submissions. We report the scores of each team, ordered by their last submission as we agreed to rank them. The shape of the points indicate in which round they submitted that predictions.

Some teams did not submit in the final rounds in some cases the final submissions were worst than the previous ones.

Here we go though the best teams as they are ranked on the figure. In all cases the write-ups need to be checked.

  • The top 8 places are stable.
  • MacBookPro did not submit in the final round

TODO: decide what to do with the teams that didnt submit in the final round. This could influence the 3rd place.
